                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">写的有些片面…但是某些方面居然还深刻…好矛盾</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1203007834">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1203007834" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1203007834" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1203007834">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63289525/">方土方</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">如果驯养了某只动物，那么无论如何都不会允许有人伤害它。这与人与人之间的关系是同一个道理，只要不认识对方就不会为对方的境遇产生太大波动。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1180617946">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1180617946" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1180617946" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1180617946">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/58017994/">无端狂笑无端哭</a>
                    <span>2017-04-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">看了几页，不认同其价值观，性别平等以及人种平等建立在都是有思想的独立个体，畜牧业为一种产业，高等生物与低等生物本就不平等。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1158766705">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1158766705" class="vote-count">0</span>
